Achievements.Name: One Day at DARPA
Achievements.Description: Complete all DARPA training exercises.

Achievements.Name: Space Normandy
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 1.

Achievements.Name: Storming Grand Hill
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 2.

Achievements.Name: I Don't Speak Kreon!
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 3.

Achievements.Name: My Way
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 4.

Achievements.Name: End to Major Combat Operations
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 5.

Achievements.Name: Survivor
Achievements.Description: Complete all Acts.

Achievements.Name: Operation Overlord II
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 1 on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Ain't Life Grand?
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 2 on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Cry on, Kreon!
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 3 on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: The High Way
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 4 on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Mission Accomplished
Achievements.Description: Complete Act 5 on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: ARS Operator
Achievements.Description: Complete all Acts on Hard difficulty or above.

Achievements.Name: Gun Runner
Achievements.Description: Scan and acquire all weapons.

Achievements.Name: King of the Hill
Achievements.Description: Level a weapon up to maximum operational capability.

Achievements.Name: Fight or Flight
Achievements.Description: Manually trigger AR Mode and destroy an enemy robot.

Achievements.Name: Adrenaline Rush
Achievements.Description: Manually trigger AR Mode and destroy three enemy robots in a row.

Achievements.Name: Going in for the Kill
Achievements.Description: Destroy ten enemy robots with melee attacks.

Achievements.Name: A Heartbreaker and Lifetaker
Achievements.Description: Destroy 100 enemy robots with melee attacks.

Achievements.Name: Helloooo, Nurse
Achievements.Description: Revive a friendly troop.

Achievements.Name: Knight in Shining White Armor
Achievements.Description: Revive 20 friendly troops.

Achievements.Name: Death Wish
Achievements.Description: Destroy three enemy robots while in damage-triggered AR Mode.

Achievements.Name: 40 Yard Dash
Achievements.Description: Maintain a Boost dash to the limit of the ARS reactor without overheating.

Achievements.Name: Home Run
Achievements.Description: Destroy an incoming missile or grenade.

Achievements.Name: Home Run God
Achievements.Description: Destroy ten incoming missiles or grenades.

Achievements.Name: Brutality Bonus
Achievements.Description: Destroy a Romanov's arms and legs, then finish it with a melee attack.

Achievements.Name: Romanov This!
Achievements.Description: Destroy a Romanov with a melee attack.

Achievements.Name: The Hand of God
Achievements.Description: Destroy two Romanovs in a row using only melee attacks.

Achievements.Name: Robots Tend to Blow Up
Achievements.Description: Destroy three enemy robots at once with one hand grenade.

Achievements.Name: Hole-in-One
Achievements.Description: Destroy a Chicane with a hand grenade.

Achievements.Name: Short Circuit
Achievements.Description: Destroy ten enemy robots that have been disabled with an EMP emitter.

Achievements.Name: Two Birds with One Stone
Achievements.Description: Destroy two or more enemy robots at once with the LFE gun.

Achievements.Name: Trick Shot
Achievements.Description: Destroy three enemy robots at once with rocket launcher splash damage.

Achievements.Name: Flash! King of the Impossible
Achievements.Description: Destroy four enemies simultaneously with the Lock-on Laser.

Achievements.Name: Piece by Piece
Achievements.Description: Destroy the arms, head, and back of an KNRB-0 Argus robot.

Achievements.Name: That Ended Up Working Out Nicely
Achievements.Description: After taking control of the enemy transport in Act 2-2, do not let a single enemy escape.

Achievements.Name: Failure Breeds Success
Achievements.Description: Destroy two Argus robots in Act 2-3 while they are in bipedal mode.

Achievements.Name: Leibniz Defense Agency
Achievements.Description: Defend the Pangloss statue in Act 3-2.

Achievements.Name: Tightrope Walker
Achievements.Description: Destroy two cannons in Act 3-3 and complete the mission.

Achievements.Name: Fisher is the Other Sam
Achievements.Description: Proceed on the monorail in Act 3-4 without being spotted by the enemy troops or searchlights.

Achievements.Name: Flyswatter
Achievements.Description: Destroy all the floating turrets in Act 3-4.

Achievements.Name: Guardian
Achievements.Description: Do not allow any friendly armor to be destroyed during Act 3-5.

Achievements.Name: Hurry the #@$% Up!
Achievements.Description: Destroy five or more enemy transports from atop the Kreon in Act 3-7.

Achievements.Name: Civil Disobedience
Achievements.Description: Ignore the elevator start order in Act 4-1. Instead, hold position and destroy all reinforcements.

Achievements.Name: Buzzard Beater
Achievements.Description: Destroy the Buzzard without allowing it to reach ground level in Act 5-1.

Achievements.Name: Smoke 'em if ya got 'em!
Achievements.Description: Destroy 10 enemies distracted by cigarettes during one mission.

Achievements.Name: Auld Lang Syne
Achievements.Description: Destroy two enemy robots who have been distracted by a cigarette.

Achievements.Name: The Best of All Possible Worlds
Achievements.Description: Find and fire upon all of the Pangloss statues hidden on the colony.

Achievements.Name: Living Legend
Achievements.Description: Complete the game without dying, regardless of difficulty level.

Achievements.Name: Tactical Challenges
Achievements.Description: Complete all of the Tactical Challenges in VANQUISH
